Class Navigation

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.ziplineproject.Navigation

  • public class Navigation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the logic needed for the robot to navigate the game field, allowing it to travel to specified points and orient itself to various angles.
